00:18:29.472 --> 00:18:30.930 align:middle line:84%
And that was without
the telephone.

00:18:30.930 --> 00:18:32.390 align:middle line:84%
I mean, I don't know
what was going on,

00:18:32.390 --> 00:18:34.680 align:middle line:84%
but I thought a little bit
of distance was a good thing.

00:18:34.680 --> 00:18:37.305 align:middle line:10%
