00:19:45.660 --> 00:19:48.098 align:middle line:90%


00:19:48.098 --> 00:19:50.140 align:middle line:84%
>> I don't know that I've
ever stopped to wonder.

00:19:50.140 --> 00:19:51.040 align:middle line:90%
It's marvelous music.

00:19:51.040 --> 00:19:51.840 align:middle line:90%
