00:20:19.110 --> 00:20:20.880 align:middle line:90%
And music does so well.

00:20:20.880 --> 00:20:24.480 align:middle line:84%
Nobody ever has
to wonder why you

00:20:24.480 --> 00:20:27.000 align:middle line:84%
