of love, life, or liberty,

00:20:27.000 --> 00:20:28.380 align:middle line:90%
or any combination thereof.

00:20:28.380 --> 00:20:30.605 align:middle line:84%
It's something that
we can all relate to.

00:20:30.605 --> 00:20:31.605 align:middle line:90%
>> A universal language.

00:20:31.605 --> 00:20:31.860 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:20:31.860 --> 00:20:32.660 align:middle line:90%
>> It is.

00:20:32.660 --> 00:20:35.210 align:middle line:84%
And as you said, from the
heart is how you sing.

00:20:35.210 --> 00:20:36.503 align:middle line:90%
